Thomas rushes to the mall using his psychic magnetism

00:07:33.518 --> 00:07:36.206
all the staff in the monitoring Room are killed

00:07:36.462 --> 00:07:40.814
Thomas knocks the killer out with a baseball bat and takes the killer's mask off

00:07:41.070 --> 00:07:45.294
to his surprise, the killer is not officer Simon but the new officer

00:07:45.678 --> 00:07:49.262
Thomas now realizes Fungus Bob has two accomplices

00:07:49.390 --> 00:07:51.438
their plan was interrupted by Thomas

00:07:51.566 --> 00:07:56.750
they killed Fungus Bob, who was tracked by Thomas, and attempted to get rid of the detective

00:07:56.942 --> 00:08:00.078
the new officer's girlfriend saw files about the attack

00:08:00.270 --> 00:08:02.766
so they caused an accident and killed the girl

00:08:02.894 --> 00:08:05.454
bodachs don't hover over Simon and the new officer

00:08:05.582 --> 00:08:08.910
which means bodachs discovered Thomas's ability long ago

00:08:08.974 --> 00:08:10.766
they just played with him

00:08:10.894 --> 00:08:15.886
thinking that his girlfriend is still in the mall, Thomas grabs a gun and rushes into the mall

00:08:16.014 --> 00:08:20.302
where he sees Viola, who didn't leave the town, and the staff from the bowling alley

00:08:20.430 --> 00:08:22.286
his dream is to become real

00:08:22.478 --> 00:08:25.422
the door to hell suddenly opens on the roof of the mall

00:08:25.742 --> 00:08:29.582
bodachs climb out of the door and take up the whole mall in no time

00:08:29.966 --> 00:08:33.294
Thomas is looking for Simon and hears people screaming

00:08:33.486 --> 00:08:36.174
people rush to the gates, but all gates are closed 

